size.description: The size of the icon, the default unit is px

gutter.description: Icon spacing, default unit is px

icon.description: When selected, the icon name or image link is equivalent to the [name property] of the Icon component(https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/en-US/icon#props)
icon.description_zh: 选中时的图标名称或图片链接，等同于 Icon 组件的 [name 属性](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/zh-CN/icon#props)

void-icon.description: The icon name or image link when unchecked is equivalent to the [name attribute](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/en-US/icon#props) of the Icon component.
void-icon.description_zh: 未选中时的图标名称或图片链接，等同于 Icon 组件的 [name 属性](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/zh-CN/icon#props)

icon-prefix.description: Icon class name prefix, equivalent to the [class-prefix property](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/en-US/icon#props) of the Icon component
icon-prefix.description_zh: 图标类名前缀，等同于 Icon 组件的 [class-prefix 属性](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/zh-CN/icon#props)

allow-half.description: Whether or not to allow half selection

clearable.description: Whether to allow it to be cleared after clicking again
clearable.description_zh: 是否允许再次点击后清除

readonly.description: Whether the score is in the read-only state, and the score cannot be modified in the read-only state
readonly.description_zh: 是否为只读状态，只读状态下无法修改评分

touchable.description: Whether you can select a rating with a swipe gesture
touchable.description_zh: 是否可以通过滑动手势选择评分

events.name: change
events.description: An event that is triggered when the current score changes
events.description_zh: 当前分值变化时触发的事件
